<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <title>Otion</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <script src="./jquery-3.6.0.js"></script>
  <% if( req.session.user_id) { %>
    <script>
      $(document).ready(() => {
        $("#sidebar").hide();
        $("#open").show();
      }
      )
    </script>
    <% } %>
      <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
          $("#open").click(function () {
            $("#sidebar").animate({ width: "toggle" }, 1);
            $(this).hide();
          });
          $("#close").click(function () {
            $("#sidebar").animate({ width: "toggle" }, 1);
            $("#open").show();
          });
          $("#start").click(function () {
            $("#sidebar").animate({ width: "30%", padding: "40px" }, 600);
            $(this).hide();
          });
        });
      </script>
      <style>
        #content {
          background-color: #fffefb;
        }

        #headline {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: flex-start;
        }

        .head_content {
          padding: 5px 15px;
        }

        .head_content:hover {
          background-color: #f7f6f3;
          text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .head_content:active {
          background-color: #f0ece3;
          text-decoration: underline;
        }

        #open {
          margin-left: auto;
          margin-right: 10px;
          background-color: transparent;
          color: #b6b4b0;
          font-weight: bold;
          font-size: 25px;
          padding: 5px 10px 5px 10px;
          border: 0px;
          border-radius: 5px;
          display: none;
        }

        #open:hover {
          background-color: #e2e2e2;
          color: #908e8b;
        }

        #close {
          background-color: transparent;
          color: #bbbbbb;
          font-family: "Gill Sans", "Gill Sans MT", Calibri, "Trebuchet MS",
            sans-serif;
          font-weight: lighter;
          font-size: 25px;
          padding: 5px 5px 5px 5px;
          margin: 13px 15px;
          border: 0px;
          border-radius: 5px;
          max-width: 40px;
        }

        #close:hover {
          background-color: #e8e7e4;
          color: #908e8b;
        }

        #start {
          margin-left: auto;
          margin-right: 30px;
          background-color: #E16259;
          color: white;
          padding: 8px 15px 8px 15px;
          border: 0px;
          border-radius: 5px;
        }

        input[type="text"],
        input[type="password"] {
          padding: 1em;
          margin: 3px 0px;
          border-radius: 8px;
          border: solid 1px #bbbbbb;
        }

        input[type="text"]:hover,
        input[type="password"]:hover {
          border: solid 1px rgb(97, 97, 97);
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus,
        input[type="password"]:focus {
          outline: solid 2px #abdcef;
          border: solid 1px #bbbbbb;
        }

        body {
          margin: 0px;
          height: 100vh;
        }

        #main_pic1 {
          max-width: 120px;
          max-height: 120px;
          padding: 40px;
        }

        #main_pic2 {
          max-width: 130px;
          max-height: 130px;
          padding: 42px 25px;
        }

        #main_pic3 {
          max-width: 130px;
          max-height: 130px;
          padding: 40px;
        }

        input[type="submit"] {
          padding: 0.5em;
          border-radius: 8px;
          border: solid 1px #bbbbbb;
          margin-top: 24px;
          margin-bottom: 15px;
          background-color: #9b9a97;
          color: white;
          font-size: 20px;
          box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 1px #bbbbbb;
        }

        input[type="submit"]:hover {
          background-color: #878785;
        }

        input[type="submit"]:active {
          background-color: #7f7f7f;
        }

        #OTION {
          font-size: 40px;
          margin-bottom: 30px;
          text-align: center;
          font-family: "inter";
          font-weight: lighter;
        }

        a {
          text-decoration: none;
          color: black;
        }

        #main {
          display: flex;
          padding: 10px 30px 10px 80px;
          align-items: center;
        }

        #icon {
          max-width: 50px;
        }

        #icon_name {
          font-weight: bold;
        }

        #login_option {
          display: flex;
          justify-content: space-between;
          font-size: 13px;
          font-weight: bold;
        }

        .link:hover {
          text-decoration: underline;
        }

        #circle {
          margin: 40px 50px 50px 150px;
          width: 200px;
          height: 200px;
          border-radius: 100px;
          min-width: 200px;
          border: solid 1px rgb(135, 135, 135);
          background-color: white;
          display: inline-block;
        }

        #sections {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          font-size: 25px;
          max-width: 99%;
        }

        #sections:hover {
          background-color: #fcf9f2;
        }

        #wrapper {
          display: flex;
          align-content: space-between;
          justify-content: space-between;
          min-height: 100vh;
        }

        #content {
          width: 100%;
        }

        form {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
        }

        #userinfo {
          margin-left: 20px;
          color: #878785;
          font-size:20px;
          width: 200px;
          line-break: anywhere;
        }
      </style>
      <% if( !req.session.user_id) { %>
        <style>
          #sidebar {
            display: flex;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            width: 0%;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #f7f6f3;
            align-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0px;
          }
        </style>
        <% }else{ %>
          <style>
            #sidebar {
              display: flex;
              flex-direction: column;
              justify-content: flex-start;
              align-content: flex-start;
              align-items: flex-start;

              width: 18%;
              min-width: fit-content;

              overflow: auto;

              background-color: #f7f6f3;
            }

            #logout {
              margin: 20px;
              background-color: transparent;
              border: solid 1px #bbbbbb;
              border-top: 1px solid #e8e7e4;
              font-size: 18px;
              padding: 5px 15px;
              color: #b6b4b0;
              text-align: left;
              border-radius: 10px;
            }

            #logout:hover {
              background-color: #e8e7e4;
            }
          </style>
          <% } %>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="wrapper">
    <div id="content">
      <div id="headline">
        <a id="main" href="/main">
          <img id="icon" src="images/otion.png" />
          <span id="icon_name" class="center">Otion</span>
        </a>
        <span class="head_content">
          <a class="link" href="/analysis/">분석</a>
        </span>
        <span class="head_content">
          <a class="link" href="/review/">복습</a>
        </span>
        <span class="head_content">
          <a class="link" href="https://www.notion.so/ko-kr/product">노션이란?</a>
        </span>
        <span class="head_content">
          <a class="link" href="https://osmin.notion.site/070e67e215274cdfae0eae368b60e7ca">ex</a>
        </span>
        <% if(req.session.user_id){ %>
          <button id="open"> &#9776; </button>
          <% }else{ %>
            <button id="start"> 시작하기 </button>
            <% } %>
      </div>
      <div id="sections">
        <div id="circle">
          <img id="main_pic1" src="images/feedback.png" alt="feedback image" />
        </div>
        <span>
          당신의 Notion 페이지를 시각적 피드백을 통해 한 눈에 파악할 수
          있습니다.
        </span>
      </div>
      <div id="sections">
        <div id="circle">
          <img id="main_pic2" src="images/review.png" alt="review image" />
        </div>
        <span>
          당신의 Notion에 담긴 정리내용들을 쉽고 간편하게 복습할 수 있습니다.
        </span>
      </div>
      <div id="sections">
        <div id="circle">
          <img id="main_pic3" src="images/pages.png" alt="pages image" />
        </div>
        <span>
          또한 당신은 동시에 여러 개의 페이지를 연결할 수 있습니다.
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Sidebar -->
    <% if(!req.session.user_id){ %>
      <div id="sidebar">
        <div id="OTION">OTION</div>
        <form action="/login_check" method="POST">
          <input type="text" name="user_email" placeholder="ID" />
          <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" />
          <input type="submit" value="로그인" />
        </form>
        <span id="login_option">
          <a class="link" href="/register">회원가입</a>
          <!-- url로 설정해주어야 접근이 가능하다. -->
          <a class="link" href="/find_idpw">아이디/비밀번호 찾기</a>
        </span>
      </div>
      <% }else{ %>
        <div id="sidebar">
          <button id="close">≫</button>
          <div id="userinfo">
            <%= req.session.user_id %>님,<br>안녕하세요.
          </div>
          <button id="logout" onclick="location.href='/logout'">Logout</button>
        </div>
        <% } %>
  </div>
</body>

</html>